{"tid":202281,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"另類病毒出現: 打爆超難 Game 才可解鎖電腦！","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T23:51:07.000Z","uid":1886,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77892ca591a997ed68def787eac6934f501d9166","tid":202281,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">另類病毒出現: 打爆超難 Game 才可解鎖電腦！[有片]<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.price.com.hk/news.php?id=7768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fnews.php%3Fid%3D7768&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=80b5d2b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.price.com.hk/news.php?id=7768</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.price.com.hk/space/news/images/20170410/bc370fc96656fd260547.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fspace%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F20170410%2Fbc370fc96656fd260547.jpg&h=2f99823b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n「勒索病毒」是近年興起的新型病毒，一旦電腦被感染就會要求向黑客付錢才能解鎖繼續用。不過最近出現一個另類勒索病毒：今次要求不是付錢，竟然是要打爆一隻超難遊戲！<br />\n<br />\n這個新病毒叫 &ldquo;Rensenware&rdquo;，中招後電腦內所有資料都會被加密鎖上。除非滿足病毒要求，否則已經變成一部「廢機」。而病毒的要求就是玩一隻叫「東方星蓮船 Undefined Fantastic Object」的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.price.com.hk/space/news/images/20170410/470fb4c90fa360364d50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fspace%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F20170410%2F470fb4c90fa360364d50.jpg&h=be1e14f2&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n這遊戲在 2009 年在 Windows 推出，是超高難道 2D 射擊 + 「避彈」遊戲。你必須以「瘋狂」(Lunatic) 難度玩，並且取得 2 億分才可解鎖。只要看一看畫面就知道要得到這個分數絕不容易，就算是高手也可能要花很長時間才能達成。<br />\n<br />\n幸好 Rensenware 開發者 Tvple Eraser 並非惡意黑客，他表示根本沒有嘗試散播這病毒，最初造出來只是想開個玩笑。之後又發放工具讓不小心中招的人可以直接解鎖。不過 Rensenware 的原始碼已被公開，說不定會有真的黑客將其加強和利用。到時或者你就要開始磨練你的「東方星蓮船」技術了！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4H2eVxy5keM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4H2eVxy5keM&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f68b3190\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4H2eVxy5keM</a></div>"},{"pid":"6f4007cf1c50a078bcd390c6ce984e507e27e715","tid":202281,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fe1db7f49cc5ac907462c0536dd4ad122f61df","tid":202281,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"Hard見到虎丸星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ccb9aede53f0044cf242d00196ad623ddb48fe","tid":202281,"uid":46459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"大佬呀點避呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb9ce294b9d336dbee1a48b8b84a45b33000723","tid":202281,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:20:44.000Z","msg":"Warning 圖係咪袁生畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5929e997fe0fcf07bd85067acf03825a84552b","tid":202281,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"講真唔玩咁難<br />\n淨係每開一個programme 都要你玩舖包剪dup <br />\n贏左先開到<br />\n輸左就del 撚你<br />\n已經夠曬仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8184eecaf22e3db47e8bbf65aa03658281060d3","tid":202281,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"有幾個fd之前成日玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4119f335dfabbe1b49170d8e7b5a94fa11f78a8","tid":202281,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:35:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cb49e94d4527233653e4f487c2935606743e874","tid":202281,"uid":70763,"